    <section id="why">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-center text-uppercase">Why Choose Us?</h1>
        <hr class="breakline">
      
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 text-justify">
            <h2>1. Absolutely free </h2>
            <p>We want to solve the issue of high textbook costs, but no way to offset these costs once the books have been purchased. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 text-justify">
            <h2>2. Eco-friendly </h2>
            <p> Instead of throwing the books away, find them a good home and have them find someone who appreciates them</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 text-justify">
            <h2>3. A worthwhile charitable cause</h2>
